##If you’re an elite sportsperson or coach

You may be eligible for an [International Sportsperson visa](/sportsperson-visa) to work as an elite sportsperson or coach.

###Eligibility

The eligibility criteria include:

+ having a job offer
+ being endorsed by your sport's governing body - you must be an elite sportsperson who is internationally established at the highest level of your sport
+ usually proving that you can speak and understand English, if you’re applying to stay for longer than 12 months

###How long you can stay

Your visa can last for up to 3 years. You can extend it as long as you’re still eligible.

After 5 years, you may be able to settle permanently in the UK.
